<br>
So my question: Do we really need so many particles? If the casting graphics were more subtle, maybe half of what they are now, would it be better? Less lag, more ppl would be able to have particles on etc...Turning particles from high to low doesnt seem to have much effect.<br>
<br>
How many of you play with your particles on? Anyone think this is a good idea?<br>
